🔹 1. Core Concepts (VERY IMPORTANT)
    These are the foundation—almost every question comes from here.
      Route:Defines message flow (from → to)
      Exchange:The message container (body + headers + properties)
      Message:Actual data inside Exchange
      Processor:Custom logic (like service layer in Spring)
    👉 Example:
        from("file:input")
           .process(exchange -> {
               String body = exchange.getIn().getBody(String.class);
               exchange.getIn().setBody(body.toUpperCase());
           })
           .to("file:output");
